  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いた……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There he is!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_002Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おや、君たち。
元気だったかい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, it's you people! You look great!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_003Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、&lt;Klarth&gt;も。
僕に会いたくなったのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even &lt;Klarth&gt;'s here! Does everyone want to meet me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>帰っていいか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is it really him?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuuru! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_010Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>で、精霊探しは
うまくいっているのかい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is the Spirit hunt going smoothly?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>実はそのことで
お願いがあって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Actually, concerning that, we need to ask you for a favor... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_012Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なるほど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_013Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだな、&lt;Klarth&gt;は
王国のお歴々の心証も
よくないだろうし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. Alvanista's kingdom doesn't exactly have the
highest opinion of &lt;Klarth&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それでおまえから
陛下宛てに手紙を
書いてもらいたいのだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Could you please write a letter to the King for us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_015Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君に頼りにされちゃ、
仕方ないな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez, if you ask it like that, then I guess I can't say no.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278176</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_016Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その代わり。
僕の研究を手伝う件、
よろしくな、&lt;Klarth&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In exchange, I want you to help me with my research.
Welcome to the team, &lt;Klarth&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_017Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルヴァニスタから返事が
あるまで一晩はかかるだろう。
それまで待っていてくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Until we get a formal reply from Alvanista,
stick around here please. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>変なの……
でも、ちゃっかりしてる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Weird guy...but he's as smart as a whip.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I guess.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>技術提供、
約束させられちゃった
みたいだしね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like you got yourself compromised into some work.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ、構わないが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not a problem.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>返事があるまで
時間があるだろうから、
私は少しぶらぶらするかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It'll be some time until we get a reply,
so I'll go take a walk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃ、ま、一旦、
かいさーんってことで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll follow suit and go take a rest myself!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_080_010_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おう、また後で</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ok! See you later, then!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
